'''ZeniMax Media Inc.'''（中文译名：泽尼麦美地亚有限公司）是美国媒体公司，通过其子公司开发并发行电子游戏。ZeniMax持有[[id_Software|id Software]]（[[毁灭战士系列|毁灭战士系列]]、[[雷神之锤系列|雷神之锤系列]]、[[德军总部系列|德军总部系列]]开发商）、[[贝塞斯达游戏工作室|贝塞斯达游戏工作室]]（[[上古卷轴系列|上古卷轴系列]]、《[[辐射3|辐射3]]》开发商）、[[Arkane_Studios|Arkane Studios]]（《[[地城英雄誌|地城英雄誌]]》、《[[魔法门之黑暗弥赛亚|魔法门之黑暗弥赛亚]]》和《[[冤罪杀机|羞辱]]》开发商）、{{tsl|en|Tango Gameworks|探戈遊戲工作室}}（《[[邪靈入侵|邪靈入侵]]》開發商）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vg247.com/2010/10/28/boom-zenimax-buys-tango-and-shinji-mikami/ |title=Boom: Zenimax buys Tango and Shinji Mikami |publisher=VG247 |date=2010-10-28 |accessdate=2012-10-18 |archive-date=2012-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001104639/http://www.vg247.com/2010/10/28/boom-zenimax-buys-tango-and-shinji-mikami/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[MachineGames|MachineGames]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.develop-online.net/news/36273/Buyout-brings-birth-of-ZeniMax-Sweden-report |title=Buyout brings birth of ZeniMax Sweden – report | Game Development | News by Develop |publisher=Develop-online.net |date=2010-11-05 |accessdate=2012-10-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009173712/http://www.develop-online.net/news/36273/Buyout-brings-birth-of-ZeniMax-Sweden-report |archivedate=2012-10-09 }}</ref>和{{tsl|en|ZeniMax Online Studios|}}。ZeniMax Media Inc.总部位于美国[[马里兰州|马里兰州]][[羅克維爾_(馬里蘭州)|罗克维尔市]]，并在北美、欧洲、亚洲和澳洲设有办公室<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.zenimax.com/profile.htm |title=ZeniMax Media Company Profile |publisher=Zenimax.com |date= |accessdate=2013-01-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209063802/http://www.zenimax.com/profile.htm |archivedate=2014-02-09 }}</ref>。

ZeniMax Media在2007年报告资产约12亿美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.docstoc.com/docs/38310700/RR-Donnelley-Private-Equity |title=RR Donnelley Private Equity |publisher=Docstoc.com |date= |accessdate=2012-10-18 |archive-date=2014-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808053544/http://www.docstoc.com/docs/38310700/RR-Donnelley-Private-Equity |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.telecompaper.com/news/prosiebensat1-hold-talks-with-us-game-producer-zenimax--577343 |title=ProSiebenSat.1 hold talks with US game producer ZeniMax |publisher=Telecompaper |date=2007-11-02 |accessdate=2013-01-23 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304154736/http://www.telecompaper.com/news/prosiebensat1-hold-talks-with-us-game-producer-zenimax--577343 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年3月21日，ZeniMax Media在位於[[達拉斯|達拉斯]]的[[德克薩斯州|德州]]北區聯邦地方法院對[[Oculus_VR|Oculus VR]]公司、Oculus VR的創辦人Palmer Luckey提出訴訟，ZeniMax Media主張Palmer Luckey非法竊取屬於該公司的[[商業機密|商業機密]]、並且違反雙方在2012年五月的技術合作過程中所簽訂的保密協定，且Oculus的母公司[[Facebook|Facebook]]在2014年收購Oculus VR的過程中對此事知情。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/5/21/5739064/zenimax-sues-oculus-vr|title=ZeniMax sues Oculus VR for misappropriation of trade secrets|publisher=Polygon|date=2014-03-21|accessdate=2017-02-02|archive-date=2022-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220125182123/https://www.polygon.com/2014/5/21/5739064/zenimax-sues-oculus-vr|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年2月1日，陪審團判決Oculus、Facebook、Luckey應支付ZeniMax Media五億美元賠償金，其中Oculus應支付二億五千萬美元、Luckey個人應負擔五千萬美元、Oculus VR前CEO Brendan Iribe需支付一億五千萬美元。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://techcrunch.com/2017/02/01/jury-awards-zenimax-500-million-in-oculus-vr-lawsuit/|title=Jury awards ZeniMax $500 million in Oculus VR lawsuit|publisher=TechCrunch|date=2017-02-01|accessdate=2017-02-02|archive-date=2017-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170201211643/https://techcrunch.com/2017/02/01/jury-awards-zenimax-500-million-in-oculus-vr-lawsuit/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年12月13日，雙方就訴訟達成了和解。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/12/13/facebook-and-zenimax-settle-vr-lawsuit/|title=Facebook 跟 ZeniMax 的專利案和解了|accessdate=2018-12-14|work=Engadget 中文版|language=zh-Hant|archive-date=2018-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181214124859/https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/12/13/facebook-and-zenimax-settle-vr-lawsuit/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年9月21日，[[微软|微软]]宣布以75亿美元收购ZeniMax Media<ref>[https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2020-09-21-microsoft-buying-zenimax-parent-company-of-bethesda-id-software-and-more-report Microsoft buying Zenimax, parent company of Bethesda, id Software and more for $7.5bn] {{Wayback|url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2020-09-21-microsoft-buying-zenimax-parent-company-of-bethesda-id-software-and-more-report |date=20220325023908 }}.Eurogamer.2020-09-21.[2020-09-21].</ref>，並於2021年3月9日完成，ZeniMax正式成為[[Xbox遊戲工作室|Xbox遊戲工作室]]的一員<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.videogameschronicle.com/news/microsoft-confirms-its-bethesda-acquisition-is-complete-and-some-games-will-be-exclusive/ |title=Microsoft confirms its Bethesda acquisition is complete and 'some games' will be exclusive |first=Andy |last=Robinson |date=March 9, 2021 |access-date=March 9, 2021 |work=[[Video_Games_Chronicle|Video Games Chronicle]] |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309164348/https://www.videogameschronicle.com/news/microsoft-confirms-its-bethesda-acquisition-is-complete-and-some-games-will-be-exclusive/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同時解散董事會<ref>{{cite web|first=Eddie|last=Makuch|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/zenimax-board-of-directors-dissolved-after-xboxs-bethesda-purchase/1100-6488918/|title=ZeniMax Board Of Directors Dissolved After Xbox's Bethesda Purchase|website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date=March 17, 2021|accessdate=March 17, 2021|archive-date=2021-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321203649/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/zenimax-board-of-directors-dissolved-after-xboxs-bethesda-purchase/1100-6488918/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
